flowchart LR
    REQ[API Request]

    REQ --> VERS{version header?}
    VERS -->|missing| DEFAULT[use default version]
    VERS -->|present| CHECK{supported?}
    CHECK -->|yes| ROUTE[route to versioned handler]
    CHECK -->|deprecated| WARN[add Deprecation header]
    CHECK -->|sunset passed| REJ[reject 410 Gone]
    WARN --> ROUTE

    DEFAULT --> ROUTE
    ROUTE --> RESP[Response]
    REJ --> RESP
